mathematica: s = {}; m = 12; Do[n = 5^k; While[n <= 5^m, AppendTo[s, n]; n *= 3], {k, 0, m}]; Map[GCD @@ # &, Partition[Union[s], 2, 1]] (* _Amiram Eldar_, Feb 06 2020 *)
